@startuml AI4Health_Architecture
!define RECTANGLE class

RECTANGLE "Existing Health Data\n(Kenya Health Info System, CSV, DB)" as DataSource
RECTANGLE "Data Preprocessing\n(app/utils/utils.py)" as Preprocessing
RECTANGLE "ML Model\n(app/models/model.py)" as Model
RECTANGLE "Prediction & Explainability\n(app/services/predict.py)" as Service
RECTANGLE "API Layer\n(app/api/endpoints.py, main.py)" as API
RECTANGLE "User Interface\n(Dashboard, Client App)" as UI

DataSource --> Preprocessing : Load & Clean Data
Preprocessing --> Model : Feature Extraction
Model --> Service : Model Inference
Service --> API : Prediction & SHAP Output
API --> UI : JSON Response (Prediction, Explanation)
UI --> API : Prediction Request (Symptoms, Data)
API --> Service : Forward Request
Service --> Model : Query Model

@enduml